TITLE: Using useSleep Hook in a React Component
DESCRIPTION: Example of how to use the useSleep hook in a React component. It demonstrates creating a button that triggers a sleep function and updates the component state.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pyr33x/rehooks/blob/main/apps/docs/content/docs/cli/hooks/useSleep.mdx#2025-04-12_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: tsx
